Anna Shaffer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anna_Shaffer 0 Anna Shaffer (born 15 March 1992) is an English actress and model, best known for her roles as Ruby Button in teen soap opera Hollyoaks and Romilda Vane in the Harry Potter film series.
